body.description: Formula 1? It’s more like formula fun with the Free Wheee-lees from B. toys! This colorful set of wooden cars comes with 6 little vehicles – 2 passenger cars, 2 race cars, and 2 pick-up trucks. Each toy car is bright, smooth, and easy for tiny hands to hold and play with. Not to mention that these timeless toy vehicles will leave your floor scratch-free! And taking this set of lil’ cars on-the-go is easy peasy – because of their small size, they can fit in any bag or purse! Play at home, take a drive in the car seat, or pack these vehicles when you jet off on a trip. Built with love and care, the wooden Free Wheee-lees are ready for hours and hours of fun, no matter where your kiddo wants to play!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Just B. you. Quirky and unique, B. toys are meant to inspire children’s individuality. Unexpected colors, intriguing patterns, sensory textures, and features that are as playful as they are educational! And the difference doesn’t stop there – our toys are timeless and meant to be passed on from one generation to the next. B. toys: Free Wheee-lees A timeless way to play, vrooming around with these colorful and classic toy cars can easily spark your little driver’s imagination. Will they hit the city streets and zoom around town? Maybe slowly drive through the countryside and admire the scenery? Or will they soar into the sky and roll all the way to the stars? No matter how your kiddo decides to ride, a ton of fun is guaranteed! 2 passenger cars 2 race cars 2 pick-up trucks

Ready to Zoom! Games Galore There are many ways to play with these little toy cars! Encourage your kiddo to come up with creative stories for each vehicle and their make-believe drivers, get together with a few buddies and race to the finish line, or take the educational route to learn about different colors and to practice counting from 1 to 6! Play & Learn Playing with the bright and colorful Free Wheee-lees is a fun hands-on and screen-free activity that will make your little driver giggle with delight – but there’s more! Vrooming and zooming around the house with these tiny hands-friendly vehicles is also a great way for your toddler to improve their fine motor skills, dexterity, and hand-eye coordination. Double the Fun! Roll right into fun with the friendly Mini Wheeee-ls! These small pull-back toy cars are ready to sprinkle some joy into playtime with their unique identities and special duties. Create a finish line, launch 2 at a time, and see who wins! Or get together with a couple of little friends and race with all of the pull-back cars.

Battat è un'azienda canadese, con stabilimenti produttivi in Cina. Presente sul mercato da più di un secolo, raccoglie 18 diversi marchi di giocattoli.B. toys è quello che mi piace di più. I giocattoli sono robusti, hanno colori sgargianti e dettagli sensoriali, mentre gli imballaggi sono riciclabili al 100%.Le macchine sono più grandi di quanto immaginassi e tutte molto graziose! Sono in legno, mentre le ruote sono in plastica rigida.Alcune (quelle a forma arrotondata) riescono anche ad entrare nell'ascensore del garage Hape e tutte vanno abbastanza bene (le ruote sono leggermente più strette) per la bisarca Melissa & Doug.Avrei preferito che fossero interamente dipinte, ma anche così le ricomprerei senz'altro!
